Package ohos.agp.text.richstyles

Enum RichStyle.TypeId

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RichStyle.TypeId>
      • ohos.agp.text.richstyles.RichStyle.TypeId
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<RichStyle.TypeId>
    Enclosing class:
    RichStyle

    public static enum RichStyle.TypeId
extends Enum<RichStyle.TypeId>
    Implements type IDs of rich styles.

    You can search for, delete, and iterate operations in the rich text based on TypeId. You can customize rich styles only by using TypeId#CUSTOM_RICH_STYLE.

    Since:
    7
